oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Vaginal Prolapse Repair
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Whitford, R. E.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: prolapsed vagina
mixed practice
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Prolapsed vagina is a problem for all of us involved in large animal practice. Our treatment procedures are probably not much difference than anyone else. We treat most of these cases in our haul-in facility at the clinic. Our facilities are not elaborate, but functional, allowing us to do about 75 % of our large animal work at the clinic. I feel this is about the only way a mixed practice can survive continuing to do large animal work.
